nd that carrier collimation is currently\nlimited by the non-linearity of the doping profile across the junction. Our\nwork provides benchmarks of the current graphene p-n junction quality and\nprovides guidance for future improvements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2018 16:43:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-01"}
